'''菲利普·菲利普斯'''（{{lang-en|'''Phillip Phillips'''}}，原名：{{lang|en|'''Phillip LaDon Phillips, Jr.'''}}，{{bd|1990年|9月20日}}），是一位来自[[美国|美国]][[佐治亚州|佐治亚州]][[利斯堡_(喬治亞州)|利斯堡]]的歌手暨唱作人，于2012年5月23日获得[[美国偶像|美国偶像]]第11季冠军。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rollingstone.com/movies/news/phillip-phillips-wins-american-idol-20120523 |title=Phillip Phillips Wins 'American Idol' |publisher=Rolling Stone |date=May 23, 2012 |accessdate=May 23, 2012}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-18185761  |title=Phillip Phillips crowned American Idol winner |date=May 29, 2012 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.nst.com.my/life-times/showbiz/home-run-1.168584 |title=Home run |publisher=New Straits Times |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121220201720/http://www.nst.com.my/life-times/showbiz/home-run-1.168584 |archivedate=2012-12-20 }}</ref>他夺冠之后发行的夺冠单曲《[[Home_(菲利·飛力普歌曲)|家]]》（{{Lang|en|''Home''}}）成为美国偶像历史上最畅销的一支夺冠单曲。<ref name="yahoo-oct2012">{{cite news |url=http://music.yahoo.com/blogs/chart-watch/chart-watch-extra-american-idol-top-dozen-171239977.html |title=Chart Watch Extra: Phillip Phillips’ Idol Record |author=Paul Grein |work=Chart Watch |publisher= Yahoo Music |date=October 24, 2012 |accessdate=October 24, 2012 }}</ref><ref name="billboard_cover">{{cite news |url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/1481573/phillip-phillips-the-billboard-cover-story|title= 'Phillip Phillips' The Billboad Cover Story |author=Phil Gallo |publisher=Billboard|date= January 7, 2013 |accessdate=January 8, 2013 }}</ref>他的个人首张录音室专辑《从月亮看世界》（{{lang|en|''The World from the Side of the Moon''}}）于2012年11月19日发行。<ref name="LATimes_Oct2012"/>

==早年生活==
菲利普斯出生在[[佐治亚州|佐治亚州]][[奧爾巴尼_(佐治亞)|奥尔巴尼]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://965tic.cbslocal.com/2012/12/08/phillip-phillips-talks-christmas-in-georgia-going-home-for-the-holidays/|title=Phillip Phillips Talks Christmas In Georgia & Going "Home" For The Holidays|publisher=|date=|accessdate=Dec 8, 2012|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130115203837/http://965tic.cbslocal.com/2012/12/08/phillip-phillips-talks-christmas-in-georgia-going-home-for-the-holidays/|archivedate=2013-01-15}}</ref>，父母是-{Phillip LaDon "Donnie" Phillips, Sr.}-和-{Sheryl Phillips}-。12岁时搬家到了佐治亚州[[利斯堡_(喬治亞州)|利斯堡]]居住。.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.albanyherald.com/news/2012/mar/07/phillips-given-key-leesburg |title=Phillips given key to Leesburg |publisher=Albany Herald |date= |accessdate=May 24, 2012}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20598145,00.html |title=Phillip Phillips Had Eight Operations During American Idol Run, His Father Says |publisher=Time, Inc |author=McNiece, Mia; Nudd, Tim |date=May 24, 2012 |accessdate=June 18, 2012}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.whitepages.com/name/Phillip-L-Sr-Phillips/Leesburg-GA/38f4z34 |title=WhitePages - Find People |publisher=WhitePages, Inc |author= |date= |accessdate=June 18, 2012}}</ref>他在萨瑟和利斯堡长大，就读于[[李縣_(喬治亞州)|李县]]高中。<ref>{{cite web |url= http://music.bluestar-tech.com/phillip-phillips-sings-lchs-2009-graduation/ |title= Phillip Phillips Sings @LCHS 2009 Graduation |publisher= Bluestar |deadurl= yes |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20131004213719/http://music.bluestar-tech.com/phillip-phillips-sings-lchs-2009-graduation/ |archivedate= 2013-10-04 }}</ref><ref name=lchs05242012>{{cite web |url=http://www.lee.k12.ga.us/lchs/index.php |title=Lee County High School - News and Events |publisher=Lee.k12.ga.us |date= |accessdate=May 24, 2012 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130714000410/http://www.lee.k12.ga.us/lchs/index.php |archive-date=2013-07-14 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name="walb"/>他毕业于奥尔巴尼理工学院的工业技术专业，但因为参加美国偶像而错过了毕业典礼。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.mysouthwestga.com/news/story.aspx?id=710580#.T1mRDfXfN-w |title=American Idol star Phillip Phillips to miss graduation |date=January 22, 2012 |accessdate=March 8, 2012 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120609024644/http://www.mysouthwestga.com/news/story.aspx?id=710580#.T1mRDfXfN-w |archive-date=2012-06-09 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>在参加美国偶像之前，他在家里开的[[当铺|当铺]]工作。

菲利普斯14岁开始演奏音乐。当时他师从于自己的姐夫，也是认识很久的朋友本杰明·尼尔。后来他表示，是尼尔激起了他在音乐方面的兴趣。<ref name="albanyuncovered">{{cite web |url=http://www.albanyuncovered.com/phillip-phillips/ |title=Phillip Phillips has hit the local the music scene like a rocket! |publisher=Albany uncoverd |date=September 13, 2011 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121008235254/http://www.albanyuncovered.com/phillip-phillips/ |archivedate=2012年10月8日 }}</ref>2009年，他和尼尔以及另一个姐夫陶德·尤瑞克组建了“菲利普·菲利普斯乐队”，并在当地的一些活动中演出。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://thealbanyjournal.com/2011/04/albany-panther-announce-tailgate/ |title=Albany Panther Announce Tailgate |publisher=The Albany Journal |date=April 29, 2011 |accessdate=June 10, 2012 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20130204045602/http://thealbanyjournal.com/2011/04/albany-panther-announce-tailgate/ |archive-date=2013-02-04 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>2010年，他在当地的一个歌唱比赛“奥尔巴尼之星”中获胜。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.mysouthwestga.com/news/story.aspx?id=620780 |title=Albany Star holds round one of competition Saturday |publisher=Fox31online |author=Ashley Knight |date=May 21, 2011 |access-date=2013-07-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140312225237/http://www.mysouthwestga.com/news/story.aspx?id=620780 |archive-date=2014-03-12 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>菲利普斯说他最爱的歌手是{{link-en|强尼蓝|Jonnny Lang}}，其他最爱的歌手还包括{{Link-en|约翰·巴特勒|John Butler (musician)}}、{{link-en|戴夫·马修斯|Dave Matthews}}和[[戴米恩·莱斯|戴米恩·莱斯]]，<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/video/phillip-phillips-american-idol-297243 |title=Phillip Phillips 'American Idol' |author= Portia Medina |publisher=The Hollywood Reporter |date=May 23, 2012 |accessdate=May 26, 2012 }}</ref>他还喜欢[[蒙福之子樂團|蒙福之子樂團]]和[[工具乐队|工具乐队]]。<ref name="albanyuncovered"/>他形容自己的音乐为“爵士和另类摇滚之声”。<ref name="THR">{{cite web |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/idol-worship/american-idol-phillip-phillips-home-single-329202 |title ='American Idol' Champ Phillip Phillips on 'Home': 'I Told Them It's Not My Single' (Video) |author=Michele Amabile Angermiller, Didi Benami |publisher=The Hollywood Reporter|date=May 22, 2012 |accessdate=May 26, 2012 }}</ref>

在参加美国偶像之前，他还曾参加了[[美国达人|美国达人]]的海选，但是未能进入决赛。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.accesshollywood.com/idol-finalists-jessica-sanchez-and-phillip-phillips-dish-on-their-americas-got-talent-past_article_65162 |title=Idol Finalists Jessica Sanchez & Phillip Phillips Dish On Their America’s Got Talent Past |author=Erin O’Sullivan |publisher=Access Hollywood |date=May 23, 2012 }}</ref>

==美国偶像==

===概况===
菲利普斯在佐治亚州[[萨凡纳|萨凡纳]]参加海选。<ref name="David Leathers Jr., Phillip Phillips Wow">{{cite news |url= http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1677513/american-idol-premiere-auditions.jhtml |date= January 18, 2012 |work= MTV |title= 'American Idol': David Leathers Jr., Phillip Phillips Wow |author= Graham, Adam |accessdate= April 27, 2012}}</ref>海选时，他演唱了[[史提夫·汪达|史提夫·汪达]]的歌曲《迷信》（{{lang|en|''Superstition''}}）。<ref name="David Leathers Jr., Phillip Phillips Wow"/><ref name="Phillip Phillips' 'Thriller'">{{cite news |url= http://blog.zap2it.com/frominsidethebox/2012/01/american-idol-phillip-phillips-thriller-superstition-win-the-night.html |date= January 18, 2012 |work= Zap2It |title= 'American Idol': Phillip Phillips' 'Thriller,' 'Superstition' win the night |author= Reiher, Andrea |accessdate= April 28, 2012 |deadurl= yes |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20120428060637/http://blog.zap2it.com/frominsidethebox/2012/01/american-idol-phillip-phillips-thriller-superstition-win-the-night.html |archivedate= 2012年4月28日 }}</ref>评委要求他用吉他再表演一首歌曲，他表演了[[迈克尔·杰克逊|迈克尔·杰克逊]]的《颤栗》（{{lang|en|''Thriller''}}）。<ref name="David Leathers Jr., Phillip Phillips Wow"/><ref name="Phillip Phillips' 'Thriller'"/>他成功晋级好莱坞赛，<ref name="David Leathers Jr., Phillip Phillips Wow"/>随后又晋级拉斯维加斯赛。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.wetpaint.com/american-idol/video/watch-phillip-phillips-perform-nice-and-slow-in-american-idol-2012-final-judgment-part-1-on-february-22/ |title=Watch Phillip Phillips Perform "Nice and Slow" in American Idol 2012 Final Judgment Part 1 on February 22  |date=February 22, 2012 |accessdate=May 24, 2012}}</ref>

2012年2月23日，菲利普斯被选入半决赛，成为25强选手之一，<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.realitytvworld.com/news/american-idol-reveals-14-of-eleventh-season-top-24-semifinalists--13164.php/ |title='American Idol' reveals 14 of eleventh season's Top 24 semifinalists |date=February 23, 2012 |accessdate=May 24, 2012 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120509225708/http://www.realitytvworld.com/news/american-idol-reveals-14-of-eleventh-season-top-24-semifinalists--13164.php |archivedate=2012-05-09}}</ref>随后由观众投票进入13强。<ref name="walb">{{cite web |url=http://www.walb.com/story/17068423/phillip-phillips-phenomenon-grows |title=Phillip Phillips phenomenon grows |date=March 2, 2012 |accessdate=March 8, 2012}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.accesshollywood.com/american-idol/american-idol-top-13-revealed_articletab_61458 |title = American Idol – Access Hollywood |date= |accessdate=March 2, 2012}}</ref>他的舞-{台}-风格被拿来与{{link-en|戴夫·马修斯|Dave Matthews}}相比较，而他也在比赛中翻唱了马修斯的一首歌《The Stone》。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://davematthewsblog.com/phillip-phillips-dave-matthews-mannerisms-on-american-idol/ |title=Phillip Phillips Dave Matthews Mannerisms on American Idol |publisher=Dave Matthews blog }}</ref>当戴夫·马修斯被问到菲利普斯对他的风格的演绎时，他表示：“他（指菲利普斯）更有力量，我不介意这点。”马修斯还表示：“他理应做得比我更出色，这样我可能就可以退休让他接管我的乐队了。”<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.vulture.com/2012/05/dave-matthews-phillip-phillips-american-idol.html |title=Dave Matthews: Idol’s Phillip Phillips Should Take Over My Band |author=Meg Miller |publisher=Vulture |date=May 2, 2012 }}</ref> 

在13强表演夜结束后，菲利普斯因疑似[[肾结石|肾结石]]被送往医院。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://abcnews.go.com/blogs/entertainment/2012/03/report-american-idol-contestant-phil-phillips-rushed-to-hospital/ |title=‘American Idol’ Contestant Phil Phillips Says He’s Fine After Seeing Doctor |date=March 8, 2012 |accessdate=March 8, 2012}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.beautymania.biz/2012/05/entertainment-paradise-phillip-phillips.html |title=‘American Idol’ winner Phil Phillips to undergo surgery, talks about health issues |date=May 25, 2012 |accessdate=May 25, 2012}}</ref>他在美国偶像期间进行了8次手术，且曾一度因病痛考虑过退赛。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://content.usatoday.com/communities/idolchatter/post/2012/05/surgery-wont-affect-idols-tour-phillips-says/1 |title=Surgery won't affect Idols tour, Phillips says |author=Brian Mansfield |work=Idol Chatter |publisher=USA Today|date=May 24, 2012|accessdate=May 25, 2012 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://music.yahoo.com/blogs/reality-rocks/phillip-phillips-comes-hiding-rocks-yahoo-music-214420559.html |title=Phillip Phillips Comes Out Of Hiding, Rocks Out For Yahoo! Music |author=Lyndsey Parker |work=Reality Rocks |publisher=Yahoo Music |date= June 29, 2012 |accessdate=August 15, 2012}}</ref>

在三强表演中，菲利普斯演唱了[[巴布·席格|巴布·席格]]的《We've Got Tonight》。他是唯一一个在整个比赛中没有进入过淘汰危险区的选手。决赛中，菲利普斯战胜{{Link-en|杰西卡·桑切斯|Jessica Sanchez}}获得冠军。<ref name="beautymania1">{{cite web|url=http://www.beautymania.biz/2012/05/entertainment-paradise-american-idol_23.html |title=Entertainment Paradise:American Idol season 11 Winner is Phillip Phillips! |author= The Beauty Mania editors |publisher=Beautymania.biz |date=May 23, 2012 |accessdate=May 23, 2012}}</ref>他在表演结束后发行的夺冠单曲《家》（{{lang|en|''Home''}}），成为了美国偶像历史上单周数字销量最高的夺冠单曲。<ref name="cauldfied">{{cite web|title=Phillip Phillips Makes 'Idol' History as 'Home' Sells 278,000 Downloads |url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/485449/phillip-phillips-storms-hot-100s-top-10-gotye-has-years-longest-running-no-1 |last=Caulfield |first=Keith |publisher=Billboard |date=May 30, 2012 |accessdate=May 30, 2012}}</ref>
